
# ReconK12

A React-based school fee reconciliation dashboard that simulates fee collection, reconciliation, penalty calculation, and administrative workflows.


## live demo

https://reconk12.onrender.com/
## Problem
Educational institutions often process fee payments through multiple payment channels, making reconciliation time-consuming and prone to manual errors.
 
Administrators must identify mismatched transactions, calculate penalties, and monitor payment status across large datasets. 

ReconK12 demonstrates a centralized workflow for visualizing and reconciling fee records in a single interface.
## Solution
ReconK12 is a client-side React application that models a school fee reconciliation workflow. The application combines administrative dashboards, fee records, reconciliation utilities, penalty calculation, and risk analysis into a unified interface.

 Business logic is implemented using reusable utility modules, while application state and simulated persistence are managed within the browser using localStorage.
