## Architecture

```mermaid
flowchart TD

    User[Administrator]

    User --> UI[React UI]

    UI --> Dashboard
    UI --> Fees
    UI --> Ledger
    UI --> Mobile
    UI --> Simulator

    Dashboard --> State[Application State]

    Fees --> FeeEngine
    Ledger --> Reconciliation
    Mobile --> OfflineQueue
    Simulator --> SimulationEngine

    FeeEngine --> PenaltyCalculator
    Reconciliation --> RiskScoring

    State --> LocalStorage[(localStorage)]
```
### Dashboard

- Administrative overview dashboard
- Fee collection summary
- Payment status visualization
- Transaction statistics

### Fee Management

- Student fee records
- Payment status tracking
- Penalty calculation
- Fee summaries

### Reconciliation

- Ledger view
- Transaction reconciliation
- Exception highlighting
- Fuzzy matching utilities

### Analytics

- Risk scoring
- Operational insights
- Summary metrics

### Simulation

- Autopilot simulation
- Offline queue simulation
- Local persistence using localStorage